With the increasing concern for security, securing identity has become an issue. Technology improve vast, fraud and forgery techniques are accompany to that technology blast. Identities are very valuable to its holder as it possess source for all official document needed. Identities must be conducted in a way to be prevented from tempering. This paper describes various techniques of authentication, authorization, encryption of identification data embedding, with comparative analysis based on their different perspectives and their obstacles. Concluding the need of an embedded and authorizing data identification module that is easy to use and can work on/off line.